summary:
I am a motivated and broadly oriented software developer with a background in the social sciences (MSc Cultural and Social Anthropology, MSc Sociology). Terms that best describe me are: Analytically strong, creative, empathetic, decicated and always eager to learn.
I am looking for opportunities to combine my background in Data Engineering with my more recently found interest in Artificial Intelligence & Machine Learning.
